{
  "info": {
    "name": "DynaDoc API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for DynaDoc Flow. Base URL: https://ddoc.fi/api\n\nAuth: Login via POST /auth/login — a JWT is set as an HttpOnly cookie (`token`) automatically.\n\nRoles: viewer < editor < admin < owner. Endpoints are annotated with the minimum required role.",
